        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "1. Overview"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The stored procedure "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "USP_ContractCreate",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " is designed to insert a new contract record into the "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Billing.Contract",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " table. It handles the creation of a contract by accepting various parameters related to the contract details and logs the operation's success or failure. The procedure also manages transaction control and error handling, ensuring that any issues during the insertion process are caught and logged appropriately."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 1
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "2. Complexity Level: Medium"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The complexity of this stored procedure is considered medium due to the following factors:"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bulletList",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "It involves transaction management with "
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "BEGIN TRAN",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ", "
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "COMMIT",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ", and "
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "ROLLBACK",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " statements."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "It includes error handling using "
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "TRY...CATCH",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " blocks."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "It logs detailed information about the operation, including input parameters and execution details."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "It uses dynamic elements such as generating unique identifiers and handling optional parameters."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
